Value INTERFACE_NAME (\S+)
Value IP_ADDRESS (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+/\d+)
Value IPV6_ADDRESS ([a-fA-F0-9:]+/\d+)
Value List SERVICE_FORBID (\S+)
Value STATUS (shutdown|no shutdown)

Start
  ^\s*interface -> Continue.Record
  ^\s*interface ${INTERFACE_NAME}
  ^\s+ip address ${IP_ADDRESS}
  ^\s+ipv6 address ${IPV6_ADDRESS}
  ^\s+service forbid ${SERVICE_FORBID}
  ^\s+${STATUS} -> Continue